internalSignatures.name: EndNote Style (RSFTSTYL variant)
internalSignatures.note: ASCII: RSFTSTYL. This is a version of the EndNote Style format, which is commonly used with EndNote 8 and later versions.

internalSignatures.name: EndNote Style (ENDNENFT variant)
internalSignatures.note: ASCII: ENDNENFT. This is a version of the EndNote Style format, which is commonly used with EndNote 7 and earlier versions
